contentrichtext.text: '''KPL''' can have several meanings: * [[Kappa Phi Lambda]], Asian American sorority * [[Karnataka Premier League]], Indian Twenty20 cricket league * [[Kenyan Premier League]], top division [[Association football|football]] league in [[Kenya]] * [[Kerala Premier League]], Indian Twenty20 cricket league in [[Kerala]]. * [[Kid's Programming Language]], commercial programming language designed by its creators to be understandable and appealing to beginning and intermediate programmers * See [[Fuel efficiency]] for Kilometers per liter, a form of thermal efficiency * [[Korean Peasants League]], NGO whose members are South Korean farmers * [[Kalamazoo Public Library]], district library in Kalamazoo, Michigan * [[Kitchener Public Library]], public library system for the city of Kitchener, Ontario * [[Kewanee Public Library]], [[National Register of Historic Places listings in Henry County, Illinois]] * [[Communist Party of Luxembourg]], communist political party in Luxembourg * [[Körber PaperLink]], based in Hamburg, Germany, is the strategic management holding company for the Körber Group’s Paper Division * [[Khaosan Pathet Lao]], the Lao News Agency {{disambig}}
